		<div id="post-293" class="post-293 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-exclusive category-entertaiment category-history category-photos tag-abandoned-city tag-chernobyl tag-soviet-era tag-soviet-architecture tag-travel-to-russia">
<div class="title_post">
<h1 class="entry-title"><img class="ttf" src="http://englishrussia.com/wp-content/plugins/ttftitles/cache/906fd00ba9915fc02e5c96fac8617d1b.png" alt="Lost City of Chernobyl" width="285" height="25" /></h1>
<span class='st_sharethis_button' displayText='ShareThis'></span>

<div class="entry-utility linest">
<div class="comment_box_ttl">
<span class="comments-link"><a href="http://englishrussia.com/2006/09/13/lost-city-of-chernobyl/#comments" title="Comment on Lost City of Chernobyl">500</a></span>
</div>
<span class="white cat-links">
<span class="meta-prep meta-prep-author">Posted on</span> <a href="http://englishrussia.com/2006/09/13/lost-city-of-chernobyl/" title="3:55 am" rel="bookmark"><span class="entry-date">September 13, 2006</span></a> <span class="meta-sep">by</span> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://englishrussia.com/author/cj/" title="View all posts by team">team</a></span></span>
</div>
