				<div class="comment-author vcard">
				<cite class="fn">MarkR</cite> <span class="says">says:</span>		</div>

		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://englishrussia.com/2006/09/13/lost-city-of-chernobyl/#comment-180635">
			February 21, 2007 at 2:40 pm</a>		</div>

		<p>The Chernobyl Exclusion Zone is a fascinating place to visit.</p>
<p>I visited the area for two days in June 2006 with a former resident of Pripyat.<br />
We got a tour of the Chernobyl Plant (including the Reactor 4 control room),<br />
several of the abandoned villages, and Pripyat.  I have posted a photo journal<br />
of my trip at:</p>
<p><a href="http://www.nikongear.com/Chernobyl/Chernobyl_1.htm" rel="nofollow">http://www.nikongear.com/Chernobyl/Chernobyl_1.htm</a></p>

		<div class="reply">
		<a class='comment-reply-link' href='/2006/09/13/lost-city-of-chernobyl/?replytocom=180635#respond' onclick='return addComment.moveForm("div-comment-180635", "180635", "respond", "293")'>Reply</a>		</div>
