		<div class="comment-meta commentmetadata"><a href="http://englishrussia.com/2006/09/13/lost-city-of-chernobyl/#comment-186881">
			March 2, 2007 at 4:00 am</a>		</div>

		<p>I WAS WONDERING HOW SAFE WAS GOING INTO THE CITY. WERENT YOU AFRAID OF RADIATION. DO YOU NOW FEEL ANY DIFFEREN ANY SIDE AFFECTS. ANYONE WHO HAS BEEN THERE CAN YOU TELL ME HOW SAFE IS IT.<br />
SORY BECAUSE MY ENGLISH IS BAD. THANKS FOR ALL THE ANSWERS<br />
