		<p>August 13,2007<br />
Earth<br />
Monday<br />
Dawn</p>
<p>Chernobyl? Lost City or City of Hope?</p>
<p>Do we derive sadness or hope&#8230;?</p>
<p>The hope in the Birth perhaps of something new or better<br />
the building on the sanity that averted the global reality<br />
of what would have or could have been much worse?<br />
Do we dwell on the omen or take courage in all those<br />
who fought for and won a battle for the dream?</p>
<p>The Dream&#8230;</p>
<p>Imagine&#8230;..</p>
<p>All we are saying is let there be harmony</p>
<p>Give Harmony a chance!</p>
<p>&#8230;</p>
<p>sir</p>

